description: This API creates a shipping document as be selected documents. The system handles requests and returns a url to show with success and error messages

parameters.name: timestamp
parameters.description: This is the timestamp of the request. Required for all requests. Expires in 5 minutes

parameters.name: access_token
parameters.description: The token for API access that verify your permission to the api. Used for handle out and display of a form

parameters.name: code_id
parameters.description: Request unique identifier for a store. Required param to avoid running duplicate. More details

parameters.name: sign
parameters.description: Signature generated by partner_id, api-path, timestamp, access_token concatenated values using algorithm. More details

parameters.name: shipping_document_type
parameters.description: The type of shipping document. Available values: SHIPPING_AIRWAYBILL_LABEL

parameters.name: marketplace_sku_request
parameters.description: List of marketplace SKUs to generate labels

parameters.name: marketplace_sku_id
parameters.description: Marketplace SKU ID in the order

parameters.name: quantity
parameters.description: Count of label that you would like to generate (Min:1)

response_fields.name: request_id
response_fields.description: The identifier of the API request for error tracking

response_fields.name: error
response_fields.description: Indicate error type if hit error. Empty if no error response

response_fields.name: message
response_fields.description: Indicate error details if hit error. Empty if no error response

response_fields.name: file_id
response_fields.description: Generated doc id which will be used for status check and download the shipping document

response_fields.name: success_at_list
response_fields.description: List Package(s) in (Marketplace) id that successful in generating shipping document

response_fields.name: fail_list
response_fields.description: List Package(s) in (Marketplace) that failed in generating shipping document

response_fields.name: id
response_fields.description: Package id or (marketplace) id that failed in generating shipping document

response_fields.name: file_grow
response_fields.description: Indicate error type if hit exist/not to grow

response_fields.name: file_message
response_fields.description: Indicate error detail if any present in error response for printing. Return error list.

notes: The documentation includes error codes and API permissions sections at the bottom. URLs for different environments (test/production) are provided at the top of the page.
